title: group_concat in SQLite for combining duplicate rows

With a normalized table split into multiple rows for repeating values, I often want to combine the redundant values into a single row when exporting for a client. In [[SQLite]], use the [[group_concat functions|https://www.sqlite.org/lang_aggfunc.html#groupconcat]]